##EXPLAIN

Design the Form (Drag & Drop Controls)
Open the Toolbox (Ctrl + Alt + X)
Drag the following controls onto Form1:
Label (lblOutput) → Set Text to "Enter your name:"
TextBox (txtInput) → Leave it empty
Button (btnShow) → Set Text to "Show Message"

## CODE

Public Class Form1
    Private Sub btnShow_Click(sender As Object, e As EventArgs) Handles btnShow.Click
        lblOutput.Text = "Hello, " & txtInput.Text
    End Sub
End Class
